WEBVTT

00:09:00.016 --> 00:09:01.836
(Laughter)

00:09:02.176 --> 00:09:04.041
Though to be honest,

00:09:04.066 --> 00:09:09.217
I regret leaving such
a super hit film over its title.

00:09:09.241 --> 00:09:10.471
So I left the film.

00:09:10.772 --> 00:09:13.231
Later I also felt a little embarrassed,

00:09:13.256 --> 00:09:14.707
and he too felt bad.

00:09:14.732 --> 00:09:17.923
So we decided to let bygones be
bygones and work on some other film.

00:09:18.195 --> 00:09:21.735
Hence, the film

00:09:21.861 --> 00:09:23.011
"Kal Ho Naa Ho."

00:09:23.177 --> 00:09:25.948
I told him that everything
else is still fine

00:09:25.973 --> 00:09:27.591
but I owe you two kuchs.

00:09:27.933 --> 00:09:29.083
Two kuchs.

00:09:29.107 --> 00:09:30.011
(Laughter)